Text: RE Followup from Iris Mack Cc Thanks for taking time out of your busy schedules to meeet with me on the th of December especially during the holiday season I enjoyed meeting some of the Research groups internal clients Hope to be able to work with you in the future Regards Iris Mack Get your FREE download of MSN Explorer at

Re FU to Dr Kaminski Enron from Iris Mackagain Thank you for your email Sorry for the phone tag and email tag I will try to call you again next week In the mean time I thought I would send you a couple of documents to give you an idea of some of the work that I have done that may be of interest to Enron The first word document is my London Busines School Executive MBA thesis relating to weather derivatives The second word document describes a hybrid derivatives structure I I workded on at BNP Paribas It has applications to the enerygy industry Because these documents are very large I will forward them in two separate emails Your comments on them would be appreciated Happy Thanksgiving Iris From To CC Subject Contact Date Wed Nov Iris Yu can reach me on my cell phone during the coming holidays Vince Get more from the Web FREE MSN Explorer download LBS thesis weather derivativesdoc

Re FU to Dr Kaminski Enron from Iris Mackagain I am visiting several family members and friends over the next few days Therefore it will be hard to contact me However next week I will be easier to reach My contact details in NYC are as follows I will be staying at the following hotels Washington Square Hotel from November th for nights Tue Wed and Thur Marriott NYC Financial December st for night Fri At any rate I will still try to reach you on tomorrow morning If all fails we will try to reach each other next week Happy Thanksgiving Iris From iris mack To Subject Re FU to Dr Kaminski Enron from Iris Mack Date Tue Nov Hi How are you Seems like we have had a bit of difficulty contacting each other Sorry I missed your call I am now in NYC until December nd I will try to call you on tomorrow morning about am Houston time Take care Iris From To CC Subject Hello Date Tue Nov Iris We are trying to reach you but we are getting error messages Please call me Vince Get more from the Web FREE MSN Explorer download
